{"tid":828799,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】兩球仔福音❗定期利息上調❗樓爆了😨❗","createTime":"2018-09-20T02:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:56:46.000Z","uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b227369dcb08ce39dad7234c97e504772b440ad0","tid":828799,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"滙豐宣布明日起上調港元、美元、人民幣定存息。<br />\n<br />\n再有銀行上調定存息率，滙豐指因應香港銀行同業拆息的變動，明日起上調港元、美元、人民幣定存息。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐宣布，上調港元定存利率5至10點子，滙豐卓越理財客戶敘造3個月、6個月、12個月及18個月定存，年息分別升至1.7厘、1.9厘、2.15厘及2.2厘；一般滙豐個人客戶可享年息則分別是1.6厘、1.8厘、2.05厘、2.1厘，起存額新資金同為1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐最新人民幣定存息率亦上調5至20點子，滙豐卓越理財客戶敘造3個月、6個月、12個月及18個月定存，年息分別升至1.8厘、2.7厘、3.1厘及3.25厘；一般滙豐個人客戶可享年息則分別是1.75厘、2.65厘、3.05厘、3.2厘，起存額新資金同為2萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，上海商業銀行亦上調人民幣定期存款息率，明日起生效，最新1個月、3個月、6個月及12個月人民幣定存，年息分別為2.5厘、3.1厘、3.2厘及3.4厘。起存額為10萬元新資金或兌換資金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180919/58700845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180919%2F58700845&d=ejPMF%2FKsVkkqkU0aRqzJe5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=0076643b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180919%2F58700845&h=3e3cf52f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180919/58700845</a>"},{"pid":"d331603239227333bfd03b834652d597aeba522b","tid":828799,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"好快活期都有 50-60 厘息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e376a6126b131df35e2d524d8002e576001520c","tid":828799,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d331603239227333bfd03b834652d597aeba522b","tid":828799,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:54:35.000Z"